Sanctum Pool
============

This project builds on the following open-source work:

- CircomStellar (https://github.com/jamesbachini/CircomStellar), MIT License.
  The Groth16-over-BLS12-381 Soroban verifier contract
  (contracts/verifier) and the snarkjs->Soroban byte conversion tool
  (tools/circom2soroban) are adapted from CircomStellar. Original
  copyright retained under the MIT License.

Design inspiration and reference (not code):
- Privacy Pools whitepaper (Buterin, Illum, Nadler, Schaer, Soleimani).
- 0xbow privacy-pools-core (association-set / ASP architecture).
- Nethermind stellar-private-payments (Stellar privacy-pool prototype).
- Railgun / Zcash Sapling (view-key selective-disclosure pattern).
